New Launch Alert ‼️ 
After a long-awaited wait, it’s finally here. 
Introducing “SENSIBIOME” — India’s first and only everywhere wash.

Created with the understanding that your skin isn’t the same everywhere — but it all deserves the same care. Sensibiome is a gentle, science-backed solution that’s made for every part of your body, including the most intimate and sensitive areas. No more switching between different products or hiding bottles at the back of your cabinet. This is body care that adapts to you.

What makes it truly revolutionary? 
💧The formula.

At the heart of SensiBiome lies a potent PREBIOTIC COMPLEX — designed to nourish and support your skin’s microbiome. 
Your skin is home to millions of good bacteria that protect, soothe, and keep it healthy. 

Harsh cleansers can strip this balance, leading to dryness, irritation, or discomfort. Our prebiotic-rich formula does the opposite — it gently cleanses while preserving the good bacteria and helping your skin thrive.

⚖️ pH-balanced to respect your skin’s natural ecosystem 
🫧 Soap-free and sulfate-free, yet still refreshingly effective 
👩‍⚕️Dermatologically tested for sensitive skin, including INTIMATE AREAS

Whether it’s your underarms, chest, vulva, groin, back, or anywhere else — Sensibiome is safe, effective, and designed for everyday use.

It’s time to stop separating body care and start embracing skincare that truly understands your body — EVERYWHERE.

Shop now! 🛍️ 🔗Link in bio
